lead_paragraph: Planned Parenthood asked a federal judge Tuesday to stop Gov. Bobby Jindal’s administration from ending Medicaid payments to the organization’s Louisiana clinics.

headline.main: Louisiana: Planned Parenthood Sues to Keep Medicaid Payments
